ITV Tour De France 2012 Stage 5 Highlights PDTV x264 AAC

Presented by Gary Imlach, Chris Boardman and Ned Boulting. Commentary: Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen. Highlights of Stage 5 Rouen to Saint-Quentin. The peloton speeds eastwards across the Somme today in a largely flat stage. Expect to see Mark Cavendish take on his former lead-out men Greipel, Goss and Boasson Hagen in a bunch sprint.
